message: |

  Usage:
    hygen feature new

  Overview:
    Generates a feature folder with subfolders for components, contexts, and hooks.

    Prompts for <Name>.

    Creates the following file/directory structure:
  
    - src
      - <Name>
        -components
          - index.ts
        - contexts
          - index.ts
        - hooks
          - index.ts
